方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=4b1e8bd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6097595b147719dfd3b444db8a7651bb67a1d86a","tid":1518180,"uid":309429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"屌 唔好叫佢女神啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3740e8dadb414ce921216ca2ed094a8a97ffd4f2","tid":1518180,"uid":122104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6097595b147719dfd3b444db8a7651bb67a1d86a","tid":1518180,"uid":309429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"屌 唔好叫佢女神啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"民主之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72433f82ada170967e1c707be6c5b57e1a889ee8","tid":1518180,"uid":270326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:22:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO平權聯署要人呀！！多你一個係好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPostcode寫00000或者852<br